  </div>

  <div class="footer-bottom container">
    <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Taian Lianchuang Textile Co., Ltd. All rights reserved.</p>
    <p>Custom Baby Sleeping Bag Manufacturer · GOTS & BSCI Certified · OEM/ODM Factory China</p>
